00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:21,784
ali, ne brini, ja imam lek
da se izborim sa njim

238
00:26:22,423 --> 00:26:23,187
To je tajna.

239
00:26:24,127 --> 00:26:26,291
Predpostavljam, zivot je boks-mec,

240
00:26:27,334 --> 00:26:28,701
i zalost je tvoj protivnik,

241
00:26:29,573 --> 00:26:30,563
Ona ima hiljade ruku,

242
00:26:31,578 --> 00:26:33,742
a ti imas samo dve!

243
00:26:34,618 --> 00:26:35,848
Ne plasi se, kada god da krene
u tvom pravcu!

244
00:26:36,322 --> 00:26:38,793
Pogledaj je pravo u oci

245
00:26:39,296 --> 00:26:40,959
proceni joj snagu,

246
00:26:41,902 --> 00:26:46,311
i onda,

247
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:48,372
dame i gospodo,

248
00:26:48,952 --> 00:26:50,683
Dobrodosli u mec stoleca!

249
00:26:51,124 --> 00:26:52,958
U ovom uglu je prelepa mlada dama,

250
00:26:53,295 --> 00:26:55,823
A u onom, je nesreca,
i publika pocinje da ludi,

251
00:26:56,236 --> 00:26:57,500
Ali, ne zaboravi jednu stvar,

252
00:26:58,441 --> 00:27:00,503
zalost je veoma jak protivnik,

253
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:03,986
Hajde da se borimo!

254
00:27:09,634 --> 00:27:10,329
Prvo ce ti napasti lice,

255
00:27:13,376 --> 00:27:13,775
to ce te boleti,

256
00:27:14,344 --> 00:27:14,777
ali, bez brige,

257
00:27:15,314 --> 00:27:15,609
nastavi da se boris,

258
00:27:16,716 --> 00:27:17,548
napasce te jos jednom,

259
00:27:18,454 --> 00:27:18,818
i ti ces pasti,

260
00:27:19,223 --> 00:27:20,692
ali, moraces da ustanes,
i popravis to,

261
00:27:21,461 --> 00:27:22,725
jer, ako izgubis u trecoj rundi,

262
00:27:24,502 --> 00:27:25,595
kod svakog sledeceg udarca,
zalost ce ti naterati suze na oci,

263
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:27,703
a svaka nezgoda ce
posegnuti za tvojim osmehom,

264
00:27:28,144 --> 00:27:29,374
a peta runda,
upasce u tvoju kucu,

265
00:27:29,814 --> 00:27:30,747
i posegnuce za srecom
tvoje porodice,

266
00:27:31,318 --> 00:27:32,446
a sesta runda,
sve,

267
00:27:32,754 --> 00:27:33,779
sve sto najvise zelis,

268
00:27:34,191 --> 00:27:35,820
dokrajcice te,
ici ce na nokaut!

269
00:27:36,163 --> 00:27:37,723
I pobednik ce biti nesreca,

270
00:27:38,067 --> 00:27:38,932
Da,
jeste!

271
00:28:01,154 --> 00:28:02,954
Jos uvek je ostala tuga
u tvom osmehu,

272
00:28:04,329 --> 00:28:07,393
Usput, sreca ti
isti tako lepo pristaje,

273
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:45,485
Ovo je moj dom!

274
00:28:46,660 --> 00:28:47,629
Tvoj dom je stvarno predivan.

275
00:28:48,832 --> 00:28:51,030
Zar ne mislis da si jako rano
dosla kuci?

276
00:28:52,574 --> 00:28:53,770
Voleo bih da je tvoj dom
samo malo dalje,

277
00:28:57,720 --> 00:28:58,916
Zeleo bih da jos malo
ostanemo zajedno,

278
00:29:11,820 --> 00:29:13,346
Voleo bih da kisa nije prestala,

279
00:29:14,793 --> 00:29:17,459
I voleo bih da ostanemo zajedno
ispod ovog kisobrana cak i kad ne bi padala,

280
00:29:31,333 --> 00:29:31,765
Ranbheer Raj!

281
00:29:32,468 --> 00:29:33,401
Mozes me zvati Raj!

282
00:29:36,712 --> 00:29:37,805
