nikada naci ovog Raja

292
00:30:11,025 --> 00:30:11,549
Jedan!

293
00:30:13,899 --> 00:30:15,026
Dva!

294
00:30:18,810 --> 00:30:19,277
Sakina!

295
00:30:21,115 --> 00:30:24,453
Ponoc je, hajde, udji!

296
00:30:25,860 --> 00:30:26,326
Ti si Sakina!

297
00:30:30,137 --> 00:30:32,938
Dobices batine, bez obzira na kolace
za praznik, ako se tvoja baka probudi,

298
00:30:33,778 --> 00:30:34,143
udji unutra, pozuri!

299
00:30:35,015 --> 00:30:35,880
Da, dolazim!

300
00:30:53,458 --> 00:30:54,357
Videcemo se sutra.

301
00:30:55,596 --> 00:30:56,062
Sutra!

302
00:30:58,135 --> 00:30:59,161
