304
00:31:01,444 --> 00:31:02,343
Bice praznik,
ako se mesec pojavi,

305
00:31:04,784 --> 00:31:05,717
ili, inace cekaj.

306
00:31:09,763 --> 00:31:10,161
Zbogom!

307
00:31:31,915 --> 00:31:32,381
Sakina!

308
00:31:34,989 --> 00:31:35,752
Sakina!

309
00:32:14,815 --> 00:32:15,248
Sakina!

310
00:35:46,277 --> 00:35:51,346
Cekao sam te cele noci, a ti si sela
pored prozora i zaspala na klaviru.

311
00:35:52,926 --> 00:35:54,262
Vi idioti ste se zaljubili.

312
00:35:54,262 --> 00:35:55,629
Sta?

313
00:36:03,818 --> 00:36:05,686
Znaci, konacno se Bog smilovao na tebe.

314
00:36:06,190 --> 00:36:07,956
U svojoj punoj milosti.

315
00:36:09,832 --> 00:36:10,892
Kako se ona zove?

316
00:36:12,205 --> 00:36:14,038
Sakina..
Sakina!

317
00:36:18,820 --> 00:36:20,050
Kako izgleda?

318
00:36:28,810 --> 00:36:32,273
