00:44:18,811 --> 00:44:20,747
Hej,slusaj...!

382
00:44:24,490 --> 00:44:25,720
Radnja je zatvorena.

383
00:44:33,011 --> 00:44:38,422
Sta?E sad, nemoj da pocnes
