385
00:44:49,783 --> 00:44:50,649
Ja sam glup...

386
00:44:51,086 --> 00:44:53,957
Vidis, meni se ovo ne svidja,
ostavi me.

387
00:44:55,030 --> 00:44:56,191
Ja sam i lutalica.

388
00:44:58,070 --> 00:44:59,003
i divlji, takodje..

389
00:45:04,151 --> 00:45:05,346
Oprosti mi.

390
00:45:07,458 --> 00:45:08,484
i tupav sam.

391
00:45:25,668 --> 00:45:27,228
Gde me vodis?

392
00:45:37,261 --> 00:45:38,058
