00:46:01,418 --> 00:46:03,685
Svet izgleda predivno odavde.

396
00:46:04,759 --> 00:46:09,396
Nista vise od tebe,
to je istina.

397
00:46:12,911 --> 00:46:15,349
Sta to radis?
Ostavi me.

398
00:46:30,820 --> 00:46:32,814
Samo sam se salio.

399
00:46:37,937 --> 00:46:42,072
Uplasio si me..
Nemoj to ponovo da radis.

