424
00:49:01,072 --> 00:49:03,043
Hajdemo na kafu.
Ne...

425
00:49:05,082 --> 00:49:06,984
Sta se desilo?

426
00:49:07,254 --> 00:49:10,661
Raj, ne mogu ici sa tobom.
Zasto?

427
00:49:10,661 --> 00:49:14,432
Moram da idem na most.
Most?

428
00:49:14,938 --> 00:49:16,100
Cekam nekoga.

429
00:49:16,575 --> 00:49:18,169
Koga, Sakina?

430
00:49:18,346 --> 00:49:21,147
Nekoga posebnog.

431
00:49:22,957 --> 00:49:24,985
Posebnog!
Koga?

432
00:49:26,131 --> 00:49:28,695
Nekoga koga puno volim!

433
00:49:35,753 --> 00:49:38,487
Sta se desilo, zasto si tako tih?

434
00:49:39,395 --> 00:49:43,200
