522
01:01:01,226 --> 01:01:01,590
Ovde.

523
01:01:03,765 --> 01:01:05,531
Ali, ne mogy te povesti
sa sobom.

524
01:01:08,375 --> 01:01:09,435
Ja radim za smrt.

525
01:01:11,382 --> 01:01:12,373
i tamo gde ja idem,

526
01:01:13,321 --> 01:01:14,517
tamo preti opasnost svakog trenutka.

527
01:01:16,361 --> 01:01:17,557
A svaka veza je slabost.

528
01:01:19,635 --> 01:01:21,299
Hocu da postanes moja snaga.

529
01:01:23,043 --> 01:01:24,342
Ali, bices moja slabost.

530
01:01:28,624 --> 01:01:29,523
Sakina...

531
01:01:31,529 --> 01:01:32,429
O Sakina..

532
01:01:33,635 --> 01:01:34,500
