676
01:13:12,739 --> 01:13:14,972
Ako se baka probudi, onda
ce to biti veliki problem

677
01:13:16,014 --> 01:13:16,947
Zbogom.
Stani, Sakina.

678
01:13:17,917 --> 01:13:18,350
Otpraticu te tamo.

679
01:13:18,619 --> 01:13:20,590
